es.fnl.fsm
Class BFSQueue<E>

java.lang.Object
  es.fnl.fsm.BFSQueue<E>

final class BFSQueue<E>
extends Object

A priority queue for breadth-first search that can backtrack the list of states that lead to some particular state.

Items are queued by their offsets, i.e., higher offsets are queued later.

Author:
Florian Leitner
